$GYEN.X to anyone new in this board. Please be careful and KNOW what you are buying if you truly decide to "invest" in this

Its 1:1 with Yen and Yen is $.0088 in american dollars

They are adding more coins in circulation(diluting) so the price will not be stable

They used the pump this morning to get alot of people to buy into the coin to then dilute more shares 

Play The Charts

Im not a bear not bull here. Im someone who doesnt want to see people lose their money by random people saying "diamond hands" and "you pussies selling for play money"

$GYEN.X people are going to hate you if you take profits. People are going to hate you for shorting. People are going to hate you regardless. Just make your money, play the chart, draw trendlines and remove all of the noise of all of the accounts saying to the moon, or its going to dump. 

Just make money
$GYEN.X For those that dont know about this coin. Just play the chart. Quick 10% from the flag breakout
$GYEN.X Play the chart. Shes trying again
$GYEN.X you want to see it hold from this downtrend break

$GYEN.X Greed will destroy your accounts

Learn to play the charts. 

You could have made an easy 35 % from the dip to 4 cents

Then rebuy when it dips

Rinse and repeat
$GYEN.X waiting to test trendline support
$GYEN.X dont listen to the clowns

$GYEN.X im happy for you shorts, for you longs, and for you scalpers. 

I made quick lunch money lol

$GYEN.X I wish people would just respect one another and stop bashing. Bulls and Bears can make money

One should stop judging the next be it if they scalp it for $50, hold it for a longer "investment", or if someone shorts it

Trade the charts and enjoy the ride!!

God Bless

$JASMY.X for the haters who hate on those posting charts. I am just trying to share ideas. When you chart something and follow the technical analysis, you are minimizing your risk and raising your reward instead of following people here with no profile picture saying "to the moon" or "get in now its going to $1"

ALOT OF SHIT CAN HAPPEN BETWEEN. Follow the charts, and if you are in it for the long run, thats great, but you have new people coming in and seeing random people saying buy now and they go ahead and buy in not knowing if its too high at that moment. 

When they buy high and it drops, they then sell because of fear of going down

When you chart a play, you remove the bullshit noise that others might throw at you. 

Stick to your conviction

$IOTX.X If you were to buy into it, you have support at around .285

No emotions, just trying to share some ideas

$XYO.X guys and gals, it is imperative for your mental health to learn how stocks work and not go by what people here are saying

You guys will stress yourselves out to oblivion looking AT.EVERY.SINGLE.MOVE

Know what you are buying, buy what you know, dont just buy because its cheap and because you see people saying its the next to run

$XYO.X If you guys didnt take profit on the rip up top, dont bitch when it dips. 

Stocks do just this, go up, then down, go up, then down. Bullish

$XYO.X Sell the rips, and buy the dips around a core. Stop bitching already lol. 

You have day traders, you have swing traders, and those who want to hold long term. 

You have to deal with the turmoil in between. 

if you have strong CONVICTION on any play, then the noise in between doesn't matter

HAPPY FRIDAY!!!!

$XYO.X people lose their minds here because it does not run straight up. lol. 

Pull backs are a part of the game, learn to trade around a core and sell into the rips and buy the dips

This has to be done in order for a healthy longer term upward move

If you say you believe in this stock like you do, turn off stocktwits and go about your day to stop stressing about every single move it makes
$XYO.X fighting to break above the middle Bollinger Band on the 15 minute chart. This is about the 5th time its doing so

$SHIB.X is not a stock for the future. This is one where you ride the momentum and dont get caught holding the bag. Always protect yourselves and never lose more than you can risk.
